{"title":"海边的等待","authors":["梁芒"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":1,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海边的等待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真不巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次来到海边正是夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除去一片黑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有些停泊在港口的星星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在夜的海边我望我等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等月儿升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望月到中天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来解夜海这个谜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谜一样的海太大太深了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能找到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡小河漂来的小纸船呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能找到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徒生爷爷的美人鱼呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我望我等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听见你涛声的私语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只闻到你呼吸的腥味儿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望呵等呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等那颗太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照蓝你身躯的那一瞬！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}